<%
// Tree Trimming Service Page with Enhanced Layout
%>

<!-- Page Header -->
<section class="page-header" style="background-image: url('/images/tree-trimming.jpg');">
    <div class="overlay"></div>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Tree Trimming Services in Gold Beach, OR</h1>
        <p>Professional Tree Trimming & Tree Pruning on the Southern Oregon Coast</p>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Main Content -->
<section class="service-detail section-padding">
    <div class="container">
        
        <!-- Introduction with Image -->
        <div class="service-intro">
            <div class="intro-text">
                <p>JT & Sons Tree Service LLC provides expert tree trimming services in Gold Beach, Oregon and surrounding communities including Brookings, Pistol River, Ophir, Agnes, Port Orford, Sixes, Langlois, Bandon, and Coos Bay.</p>
                <p>With over 30 years of experience in the tree industry, our family-owned company specializes in professional tree trimming, pruning, and limb removal to improve the health, safety, and appearance of your trees. Regular trimming helps remove dead or damaged branches, encourages healthy growth, and prevents limbs from becoming hazards to homes, vehicles, or power lines.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="intro-image">
                <img src="/images/services-bg.jpg" alt="Tree Trimming Service" class="rounded-image">
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Why Choose Us -->
        <div class="content-container">
            <h2>Why Choose Our Tree Trimming Services</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Healthier Trees</strong> – Regular tree pruning helps remove diseased or dead branches while promoting strong and healthy tree growth.</li>
                <li><strong>Improved Safety</strong> – Overgrown or damaged limbs can fall during storms and cause serious damage. Our services reduce the risk of falling branches and property damage.</li>
                <li><strong>Better Curb Appeal</strong> – Properly trimmed trees improve the appearance of your landscape and increase the overall beauty and value of your property.</li>
                <li><strong>Experienced Local Tree Professionals</strong> – With decades of experience, our team understands the unique needs of coastal trees and landscapes.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Services Include + Image Row -->
        <div class="service-include-row">
            <div class="service-list">
                <h2>Our Tree Trimming Services Include</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>Tree pruning and shaping</li>
                    <li>Deadwood removal</li>
                    <li>Tree thinning</li>
                    <li>Limb removal</li>
                    <li>Storm damage trimming</li>
                    <li>Tree topping when necessary</li>
                    <li>Large tree trimming</li>
                    <li>Preventative maintenance trimming</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="service-image">
                <img src="/images/treaming2.jpg" alt="Tree Pruning" class="rounded-image">
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Process -->
        <div class="content-container">
            <h2>Our Tree Trimming Process</h2>
            <ol>
                <li><strong>Tree Assessment</strong> – We inspect the tree's health, structure, and surroundings to determine the safest and most effective trimming approach.</li>
                <li><strong>Professional Tree Trimming</strong> – Our team carefully trims branches to remove deadwood, improve tree structure, and encourage healthy growth while maintaining natural beauty.</li>
                <li><strong>Property Protection</strong> – We use professional techniques and equipment to ensure your home, landscape, and nearby structures remain protected.</li>
                <li><strong>Cleanup & Final Inspection</strong> – After completing the trimming, we remove debris and leave your property clean and safe.</li>
            </ol>
        </div>

        <!-- Closing Text -->
        <div class="content-container">
            <p>If you are looking for tree trimming services near Gold Beach, Brookings, or Port Orford, JT & Sons Tree Service LLC is your trusted local tree care company.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Contact Info Box -->
        <div class="contact-info-box">
            <h3>Call today for a free estimate.</h3>
            <p>
                <i class="fas fa-phone-alt"></i> Office: <a href="tel:<%= sitePhone %>"><%= sitePhone %></a><br>
                <i class="fas fa-mobile-alt"></i> Cell/Text: <a href="tel:<%= siteCell %>"><%= siteCell %></a><br>
                <i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> Email: <a href="mailto:<%= siteEmail %>"><%= siteEmail %></a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>